obfuscation: Who 'll it be ?
original: Who'll it be?

obfuscation: Ah , it 's Fred Nicholls , maybe .
original: Ah, it's Fred Nicholls, maybe.

obfuscation: Eileen 's young man , Doctor , that she 's engaged to marry , as you might say .
original:
Eileen's young
man, Doctor, that she's engaged to marry, as you might say.

obfuscation: H'mm -- yes -- she spoke of him .
original: H'mm--yes--she spoke of him.

obfuscation: I had a mind to phone to your house , but I was n't wishful to disturb you , knowin ' you 'd be comin ' to call to-night .
original:
I had a mind to phone to your house, but I
wasn't wishful to disturb you, knowin' you'd be comin' to call
to-night.

obfuscation: It 's nothing serious , I hope .
original: It's nothing serious, I hope.

obfuscation: Ah , who knows ?
original: Ah, who knows?

obfuscation: Here 's the doctor .
original: Here's the doctor.

obfuscation: You 've not met him ?
original:
You've not
met him?

obfuscation: I have n't had the pleasure .
original: I haven't had the pleasure.

obfuscation: Of course , I 've heard -- -- It 's Doctor Gaynor .
original:
Of course, I've heard----

It's Doctor Gaynor.

obfuscation: This is Fred Nicholls , Doctor .
original: This is Fred Nicholls, Doctor.

obfuscation: Sit down , Fred , that 's a full lad , and be talkin ' to the Doctor a moment while I go upstairs and see how is Eileen .
original:
Sit down, Fred, that's a
good lad, and be talkin' to the Doctor a moment while I go upstairs and
see how is Eileen.

obfuscation: She 's all alone up there .
original: She's all alone up there.

obfuscation: Certainly , Mr. Carmody .
original: Certainly, Mr. Carmody.

obfuscation: Go ahead -- and tell her how sorry I am to determine she 's under the weather .
original:
Go ahead--and tell her how sorry I am
to learn she's under the weather.

obfuscation: I will so .
original: I will so.

obfuscation: Do you happen to be any relative to the Albert Nicholls who is superintendent over at the Downs Manufacturing Company ?
original:
Do you happen to be any relative to the Albert Nicholls who is superintendent
over at the Downs Manufacturing Company?

obfuscation: He 's sort of a near relative -- my father .
original: He's sort of a near relative--my father.

obfuscation: Ah , yes ?
original: Ah, yes?

obfuscation: I work for the Downs Company myself -- bookkeeper -- -- Miss Carmody -- the sick girl upstairs -- she had a position there also , did n't she , before her mother died ?
original:
I work for the Downs Company
myself--bookkeeper----

 Miss Carmody--the sick girl upstairs--she had a position there
also, didn't she, before her mother died?

obfuscation: Yes .
original: Yes.

obfuscation: She had a job as stenographer for a time .
original: She had a job as stenographer for a time.

obfuscation: When she graduated from the business college course -- I was already working at the Downs -- and through my father 's influence -- you understand .
original:
When she
graduated from the business college course--I was already working at
the Downs--and through my father's influence--you understand.

obfuscation: She was getting on finely , besides , and liked the work .
original: She was getting on finely, too, and liked the work.

obfuscation: It 's besides bad -- her mother 's death , I mean -- forcing her to give it up and come home to take care of those kids .
original:
It's too bad--her mother's death, I mean--forcing her to give it up and
come home to take care of those kids.

obfuscation: It 's a damn shame .
original: It's a damn shame.

obfuscation: That 's the main cause of her breakdown .
original: That's the main cause of her breakdown.

obfuscation: I 've noticed she 's been looking badly lately .
original: I've noticed she's been looking badly lately.

obfuscation: So that 's the trouble ?
original:
So
that's the trouble?

obfuscation: Well , it 's all her father 's fault -- and her own , besides , because whenever I raised a kick about his making a slave of her , she always defended him .
original:
Well, it's all her father's fault--and her own,
too, because whenever I raised a kick about his making a slave of her,
she always defended him.

obfuscation: Between us , Carmody 's as selfish as they make 'em , if you want my opinion .
original:
Between us, Carmody's as selfish as they make 'em,
if you want my opinion.
